"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/finding-w-h-hudson-review-the-enigmatic-birdman-bcff07e1?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">&#39;Finding WH Hudson&#39; Review: The Enigmatic Birdman</a> </h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/finding-w-h-hudson-review-the-enigmatic-birdman-bcff07e1"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-833372?width=700&amp;height=467" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">Conor Mark Jameson</span></div></div></div><p> The mysterious, contradictory life of the man who devoted himself to the preservation of England&#39;s birds. <em>Review by Christoph Irmscher</em></p><p> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/finding-w-h-hudson-review-the-enigmatic-birdman-bcff07e1?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">Read the review</a> </p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/childrens-books-bereft-bewildered-and-eager-to-remember-73aca8da?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">Children&#39;s Books: <strong>Bereft, Bewildered and Eager to Remember</strong></a> </h3><div class="media-object scope-
